title: Savaal
subTitle: Brothers Shankar and Raja decide to go to the city for better opportunities post their mother's death. However, they get separated while travelling on a goods train.

title: Adada Enna Azhagu
subTitle: Vasan falls in love with Nisha, the daughter of a politician. When Nisha's father learns about their feelings for each other, he ensures that they do not meet again.

title: Aarumaname
subTitle: When Moorthy, a government officer, dies under mysterious circumstances, his brother, Vaithi, struggles to unravel the truth behind Moorthy's murder.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Super Kudumbam
subTitle: Arun pretends to be married in order to get a house for rent. He picks Shanthi, an uncouth slum girl, to act as his wife. Eventually, circumstances change and they get actually married.

title: Manaivi Solle Manthiram
subTitle: Selvi and Dr Thyagu fall in love and get married, but she is shocked by his family's extravagant spending. Concerned, she warns her husband about their overspending and decides to teach them a lesson.

title: Jore
subTitle: Sakthi falls in love with the daughter of a corrupt politician and later competes with her brother, Vijay, at the college election. Things escalate when Vijay loses and his father gets furious.

title: Oorkavalan
subTitle: Despite protests, Kangeyan helps his brother marry a girl who is engaged to another man. But his brother is soon killed. Trouble ensues when Kangeyan decides to get his brother's widow re-married.

title: Maayandi Kudumbatthar
subTitle: A property dispute ruins the relationship between two brothers, Mayandi and Virumandi. Matters become worse when Mayandi dies and Virumandi's son seeks revenge on his family.

title: Pattiyal
subTitle: Two best friends Kosi and Selvam are contract killers who are given targets by Sami. They fall in love, but their profession becomes a hurdle and the two cannot lead normal lives.

title: Kovil Yanai

title: Sonnalthan Kaadhala
subTitle: Roja, a part-time singer, works at a finance company where her colleague, Murali, is madly in love with her. However, Roja rejects his proposal as she is the sole breadwinner of her large family.

title: Aduthathu Albert
subTitle: Although Albert, a Christian boy, and Radha, a Brahmin girl, hate each other, they decide to help their respective sister and brother who are in love.

title: Naan Sivappu Manithan

title: Ambigai Neril Vanthaal
subTitle: After a lot of persuasion, Devaki agrees to marry Ravi. However, the marriage becomes a bitter struggle for her when she comes to know that Ravi is a drunkard and a womaniser.

title: Vettri Kani

title: Fillers

title: Bose
subTitle: When the man who hired him turns out to be a criminal, Bose loses his temper and shoots him. However, this action bears heavy consequences on his personal life.

title: Ethir Kaatru
subTitle: A dubious financial company uses an unemployed youth as a scapegoat to conceal their fraudulent business. However, his suspicious death compels a journalist to expose the firm's deceptive practices.

title: Makkal Veeran

title: Naaigal Jaakirathai
subTitle: A police officer enlists the help of a trained military dog in order to locate the whereabouts of his wife, who is kidnapped.

subTitle: Akil, a restaurateur from Singapore, is taken aback after learning that he has been adopted and sets out on a journey to Chengalpet in order to find his biological parents.
